 and molecular phylogenetics in the identification of species and supports a combined approach to this problem.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Jarr\u00edn-V, Pablo", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Clare, Elizabeth L.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/f2767de9017424f470c95b469af0190c", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/d9dba549b3846bf784849e69abcb575c6943bd89698a511811a4d7e3b0c15bb3", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/QUI4YCSI", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/QUI4YCSI", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/b35fa1e23db181e13ee4e640ec2166e9!/b201739-204218", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "title": "Zootaxa", "volume": "3630"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/f2767de9017424f470c95b469af0190c"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:QUI4YCSI"}, {"identifier": "10.11646/zootaxa.3630.1.7"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13520576"}}]}}, "title": "Systematics of Sturnira (Chiroptera: Phyllostomidae) in Ecuador, with comments on species boundaries", 